},{"pid":"55a719276245da40c2f853aed651d351c7aaf12e","tid":1251572,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7173c0e650ce6eb04c06468124d72af8195c8c2d","tid":1251572,"uid":170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:28:40.000Z","msg":"我都覺得係等華南地區分裂出黎先有機會獨立"},{"pid":"b0eb8b43cf2f699a527d7ec63c6aace657baeb96","tid":1251572,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"<code>我冇嘢講</code>"},{"pid":"3de18b38dce2a452dbe4a67c5efc3d42cb852c2a","tid":1251572,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4da5c0e503e032f04bbacee86ba4617aeb98a3","tid":1251572,"uid":36148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:27:52.000Z","msg":"認同。香港更需要輸出革命，輸出混亂。 現時做的係播種，等待時機配合，一定會長出芽。理得中共天下太平定萬民怒火中燒，只要中共一日重想要同國際trade and deal就一定有國際時機令中共解體之火燃起。到時種子已發芽成長，助長火勢。<br />\n<br />\n喱代的中國人都未配得上真民主，但作為香港獨立或城邦自治的燃料就十分適合。"}]}